'''借方'''（{{lang-en|debit}}，简记为{{lang|en|Dr.}}）与'''贷方'''（{{lang-en|credit}}，简记为{{lang|en|Cr.}}）是[[复式记账法|复式记账法]]中交易[[分录|分录]]时使用的概念，其中借方位于T型账户的左边，贷方位于T型账户的右边。一般而言，资金运用账户的借方与资金来源账户的贷方登记增加数。每笔交易的借方总额与贷方总额必定相等。<ref>{{cite web|title=Debit Credit Rules|url=http://accountingexplained.com/financial/introduction/debit-credit-rules|work=Accounting Explained|publisher=AccountingExplained.com|accessdate=4 August 2011|archive-date=2011-10-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111008034548/http://accountingexplained.com/financial/introduction/debit-credit-rules|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Making sense of Debits and Credits in Accounting |url=http://basicaccountingconcepts.wordpress.com/2012/03/31/making-sense-of-debits-and-credits-in-accounting/ |accessdate=5 May 2013 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130710235821/http://basicaccountingconcepts.wordpress.com/2012/03/31/making-sense-of-debits-and-credits-in-accounting/ |archivedate=2013年7月10日 }}</ref>

一个账户中借方总额与贷方总额的差异为账户余额（{{lang|en|balance}}）。如果账户的借方总额超过贷方总额，则称账户有借方余额。反之，则称账户有贷方余额。对于公司整体而言，借方余额合计数与贷方余额合计数必须相同。<ref>{{cite book|last1=Larson|first1=Kermit|last2=Jensen|first2=Tilly|year=2005|title=Fundamental Accounting Principles|url=https://archive.org/details/fundamentalaccou0000lars_j1f8|publisher=McGraw-Hill Ryerson|isbn=0-07-091649-7}}</ref>

